<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <style>
            .jumbotron {
                margin: 64px;
                padding: 2px,8px,2px,8px;
                background-image: url('../../Content/Images/Head.jpg');
                background-size:100%;
                color:white;
            }
            body{
                background-color: antiquewhite;
            }
            .h1{
            font-family:"Comic Sans MS", cursive, sans-serif;  
            font-style: italic;
            color:white;
            
            }
            .lead{
            color: #800000;
            font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;
            font-size:10px;
            color:white;
            
            }
            .h2{
                font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;
                font-size: 22px;
                color:antiquewhite;
                border-color:#1B7E62;
                background-color:#1B7E62;
                border-style:unset;
                border-radius: 25px;
                text-align:center;
            }
            p{
                font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            /*.mySlides {display: none}*/
            img {
                vertical-align: middle;
                display: block;
                margin-left: auto;
                margin-right: auto;
            }

            /* Slideshow container */
            .slideshow-container {
                max-width: 644px;
                position: relative;
                margin: auto;
            }

            /* Next & previous buttons */
            .prev, .next {
                cursor: pointer;
                position: absolute;
                top: 50%;
                width: auto;
                padding: 16px;
                margin-top: -22px;
                color: white;
                font-weight: bold;
                font-size: 18px;
                transition: 0.6s ease;
                border-radius: 0 3px 3px 0;
                user-select: none;
            }

            /* Position the "next button" to the right */
            .next {
                right: 0;
                border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px;
            }

                /* On hover, add a black background color with a little bit see-through */
                .prev:hover, .next:hover {
                    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
                }

            /* Caption text */
            .text {
                color: #3d5c5c;
                font-family: "lucida sans unicode", "lucida grande", sans-serif;
                font-size: 15px;
                font-style: italic;
                padding: 8px 12px;
                position: absolute;
                bottom: 8px;
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }

            /* Number text (1/3 etc) */
            .numbertext {
                color: #3d5c5c;
                font-size: 12px;
                padding: 8px 12px;
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
            }

            /* The dots/bullets/indicators */
            .dot {
                cursor: pointer;
                height: 15px;
                width: 15px;
                margin: 0 2px;
                background-color: #bbb;
                border-radius: 50%;
                display: inline-block;
                transition: background-color 0.6s ease;
            }

                .active, .dot:hover {
                    background-color: #717171;
                }

            /* Fading animation */
            .fade {
                -webkit-animation-name: fade;
                -webkit-animation-duration: 1.5s;
                animation-name: fade;
                animation-duration: 1.5s;
            }

            @@-webkit-keyframes fade {
                from {
                    opacity: .4
                }

                to {
                    opacity: 1
                }
            }

            @@keyframes fade {
                from {
                    opacity: .4
                }

                to {
                    opacity: 1
                }
            }

            /* On smaller screens, decrease text size */
            @@media only screen and (max-width: 300px) {
                .prev, .next, .text {
                    font-size: 11px
                }
            }
        </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <h2 class="h1">Hungry Souls</h2>
        <p class="lead">
            Hungry Souls is a local restaurant that serves Café Food, Fusion, Coffee and Tea.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="slideshow-container">

        <div class="mySlides fade">
            <div class="numbertext">1 / 3</div>
            <img src="~/Content/Images/sidebar1.jpg" height="350" style="width:100%">
            <div class="text">Burgurs</div>
        </div>

        <div class="mySlides fade">
            <div class="numbertext">2 / 3</div>
            <img src="~/Content/Images/sidebar2.jpg" height="350" style="width:100%">
            <div class="text">Pancakes</div>
        </div>

        <div class="mySlides fade">
            <div class="numbertext">3 / 3</div>
            <img src="~/Content/Images/sidebar3.jpg" height="350" style="width:100%">
            <div class="text">Coffee Drinks</div>
        </div>

        <a class="prev" onclick="plusSlides(-1)">&#10094;</a>
        <a class="next" onclick="plusSlides(1)">&#10095;</a>

    </div>
    <br>

    <div style="text-align:center">
        <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(1)"></span>
        <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(2)"></span>
        <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(3)"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3 class="h2">Drinks</h3>
        <p>We provide a wide range of coffe drinks.</p>
        <p>Brewed Coffee, Caffè Latte, Caramel Macchiato, Espresso...</p>
        <p>Also other beverages: smoothie, hot chocolate... </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3 class="h2">Food</h3>
        <p>Our food menu are known for flavour combinations and theatrical presentations. The notorious signature croissant burger is overflowing with soft shell crab, chipotle mayo, pickled cucumber, smoked eel, fried egg, chorizo crumb and buttery croissant.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3 class="h2">Dine in</h3>
        <p>Reservations are strongly recommended in order to avoid waiting for a long time.</p>
        <p>We accept table bookings and private party.</p>
        <p>Reserve your spots at: </p>
            <a href="/Bookings/Create" style="color:azure">
                <div type="button" style="background-color: #1B7E62; padding: 5px 5px;text-align: center;font-size: 16px; color: antiquewhite; border-radius: 12px;">
                Reservation
                </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3 class="h2">Chat with Us to Know More</h3>
        <p>If you don't want to call us or send emails, you can try online chat!</p>
        <p>Click here to chat: </p>
        <a href="/Home/Chat" style="color:azure">
            <div type="button" style="background-color: #1B7E62; padding: 5px 5px;text-align: center;font-size: 16px; color: antiquewhite; border-radius: 12px;">
                Chat
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <script>
        var slideIndex = 0;
        showSlides();

        function showSlides() {
            var i;
            var slides = document.getElementsByClassName("mySlides");
            var dots = document.getElementsByClassName("dot");
            for (i = 0; i < slides.length; i++) {
                slides[i].style.display = "none";
            }
            slideIndex++;
            if (slideIndex > slides.length) { slideIndex = 1 }
            for (i = 0; i < dots.length; i++) {
                dots[i].className = dots[i].className.replace(" active", "");
            }
            slides[slideIndex - 1].style.display = "block";
            dots[slideIndex - 1].className += " active";
            setTimeout(showSlides, 3750);
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>
